The Herald Prosper Dembedza A suspected serial rapist who allegedly raped eight teenagers in Glenview at Churu Farm in Harare has appeared at the Harare Magistrates Court. Chrispen Bonda (35) from Rugare Harare was facing 14 counts of rape when he appeared before Harare Magistrate Mrs Marehwanazvo Gofa. He was remanded in custody and advised to apply for bail at the High Court.